acceptance_criteria: suggested_retry renders boolean (arity-0) flags bare (--force) and only value-taking flags with a placeholder; repro from GH-500 (pm close <id> done twice) yields a suggestion that succeeds verbatim; regression test covers boolean and value flags in suggested_retry; GH-500 closed with a comment linking the fix
